[[File:Werner Uebelmann.jpg|thumb|200px|{{Center|Uebelmann on 30 March 2008.}}]]

'''Werner J. Uebelmann''' (16 March 1921 – 1 March 2014) was a Swiss entrepreneur and writer. He was best known for his large collection of [[cactus]]. He was born in [[Aarau]], Aargau.

Uebelmann died on 1 March 2014 in [[Muri]], Aargau. He was 92 years old.<ref>[http://www.wohlen.ch/de/aktuelles/aktuellesinformationen/?action=showinfo&info_id=236042   Bestattungsanzeige Werner Uebelmann]</ref>
<ref>[http://kaktuszgyujtok.hu/kvo/2014-3/memoriam-werner-j-uebelmann In memoriam Werner J. Uebelmann]</ref>

